extends layouts/main

block content
  .legal-container
    .container
      h1 Privacy Policy
      p.last-updated Last Updated: November 15, 2025
      
      .policy-section
        h2 1. Introduction
        p CivicaLex ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our platform.
      
      .policy-section
        h2 2. Information We Collect
        h3 Personal Information
        ul
          li Name, email address, phone number
          li Postal address
          li Account credentials (encrypted)
        
        h3 Legal Information
        ul
          li Case details and documents
          li Petition information
          li Legal consultation records
        
        h3 Technical Information
        ul
          li IP address, browser type, device information
          li Usage data and analytics
          li Cookies and similar technologies
      
      .policy-section
        h2 3. How We Use Your Information
        ul
          li Providing legal information and services
          li Managing your account and cases
          li Communicating with you about services
          li Improving our platform
          li Complying with legal obligations
      
      .policy-section
        h2 4. Data Security
        p We implement industry-standard security measures including:
        ul
          li Encryption of sensitive data
          li Secure server infrastructure
          li Regular security audits
          li Access controls and authentication
      
      .policy-section
        h2 5. Data Retention
        p We retain your personal data only as long as necessary for the purposes outlined in this policy or as required by law.
      
      .policy-section
        h2 6. Your Rights
        ul
          li Access your personal data
          li Correct inaccurate data
          li Request deletion of data
          li Object to data processing
          li Data portability
      
      .policy-section
        h2 7. Third-Party Services
        p We may use third-party services for:
        ul
          li Payment processing
          li Analytics
          li Communication services
        p These services have their own privacy policies.
      
      .policy-section
        h2 8. Cookies
        p We use cookies to enhance user experience. You can control cookie preferences through your browser settings.
      
      .policy-section
        h2 9. Changes to Privacy Policy
        p We may update this policy periodically. We will notify users of significant changes via email or platform notification.
      
      .policy-section
        h2 10. Contact Us
        p For privacy concerns, contact us at:
        p Email: privacy@civicalex.in
        p Phone: +91 98765 43210